criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  PTSD;

          -  PCL great or equal to 44;

          -  Survivor of the Cambodian genocide;

          -  At least 7 years old at the time of the Cambodian genocide

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant;

          -  Active suicidality;

          -  Mental retardation;

          -  Organic mental disorder;

          -  Bipolar disorder;

          -  Alcohol dependence;

          -  Marijuana dependence;

          -  Unable to give conformed consent
